;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;即为 $$\frac {u-n\mu}{\sqrt {n}・\sigma} \sim N (0,1) \Rightarrow \frac {\frac {1}{n} u-\mu}{\sigma / \sqrt {n}} \sim N (0,1) \Rightarrow \frac {\overline {x}-\mu}{\sigma / \sqrt {n}} \sim N (0,1) $$$$\overline {x} \sim N (\mu,\sigma^2/n)$$&lt;/p&gt;
